headline.print_headline: Karlsson Scores in OT as Senators Beat Canucks 4-3
headline.main: Karlsson Scores in OT as Senators Beat Canucks 4-3

lead_paragraph: Erik Karlsson scored 1:21 into overtime to give the Ottawa Senators a 4-3 victory over the Vancouver Canucks on Sunday night.
